snippet: Louis Oosthuizen made birdies on 8 of the first 10 holes, including seven in a row, on his way to an eight-under-par 63 in the third round of the Deutsche Bank Championship.
abstract: Louis Oosthuizen takes third-round lead at the Deutsche Bank Championship golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: Louis Oosthuizen made birdies on 8 of the first 10 holes, including seven in a row, on his way to an eight-under-par 63 in the third round of the Deutsche Bank Championship.

headline.seo: Golf — Oosthuizen Takes Lead Over McIlroy
headline.main: Oosthuizen Catches McIlroy With Early Flurry of Birdies
headline.print_headline: Oosthuizen Catches McIlroy With Early Flurry of Birdies
